   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String ` A plain reading of r. 5(a) of Schedule I makes it clear that in order to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `attract the applicability of that provision the amount should firstly be an expenditure or allow'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ance. Secondly, it should be one not admissible under the provisions of ss. 30 to 43A. If the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `amount is not an expenditure or allowance, the question of testing its eligibility for adjustment '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 64>
   <String `by reference to r. 5(a) of Schedule I would not arise at all : '>
