   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `Where, upon the said investigation, the Tax Recovery Officer is satisfied '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that, for the reason stated in the claim or objection, such property was not, at the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `said date, in the possession of the defaulter or of some person in trust for him or '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `in the occupancy of a tenant or other person paying rent to him, or that, being in '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the possession of the defaulter at the said date, it was so in his '>
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `possession, not on '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `his own account or as his own pro'>
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `perty, but on account of or in trust for some '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `other person, or partly on his own account and partly on account of some other '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `person, the Tax Recovery Officer shall make an order releasing the property, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `wholly or to such extent as he thinks fit, from attachment or sale.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
   <ElementEnd `Subrule'>
  > # end of ParaLine
