   <String `Protection for bona fide purchaser of property at auction :'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Title'>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 2215531>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String ` The law makes a clear dis'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tinction between a stranger who is a bona fide purchaser of the property at an auction sale '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and the decree-holder who purchases at the auction where agricultural lands owned by the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `partners of a firm were brought to sale in public auction in proceedings under Schedule II to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the Income-tax Act, 1961, and the sale to an independent purchaser, who offered the highest '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `price, was confirmed, the bona fide purchaser of the property in the valid auction could not be '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `disturbed as according to an established principle of law a third party auction purchaser '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `continues to be protected notwithstanding that the underlying decree might be set aside : '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
