   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `A defaulter released from detention under this rule shall not, merely by reason of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `his release, be discharged from his liability for the arrears ; but he shall not be liable to be re-'>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `arrested under the certificate in execution of which he was detained in the civil prison.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
