   <String `When a provident fund is exempted under '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `section 17(1) of the Employees’ Provident Funds and (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act, 1952, it '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `is implicit that it is not established under the Employees’ Provident Funds Scheme, 1952. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Therefore, such exempted provident fund must be expressly recognised by the Commis'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `sioner under the Income-tax Act before it can enjoy benefits of a “recognised provident fund” '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `under the Act.'>
