   > # end of Font
   <String `Polyurethane foam :'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Title'>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 68838003>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String ` The assessee manufactured polyurethane foam and supplied it in '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `different sizes and designs to the assembly operator, and it was ultimately used for car seats. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `The assessee did not undertake any further process for the end product, namely, car seats. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `The polyurethane foam supplied in different designs and sizes was used as ingredient by oth'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ers, namely, assembly operators for the car seats. Merely because the assessee used the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `chemicals and ultimately what was manufactured was polyurethane foam and that was used '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `by assembly operators after the process of moulding as car seats, it could not be said that the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `end product manufactured by the assessee was car seats or automobile seats. When the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `article manufactured by the assessee, namely, polyurethane foam, was an article classifiable '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `in the Eleventh Schedule (entry 25), considering section 80-IB(2)(iii), the assessee was not '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `entitled to the benefit under section 80-IB of the Act : '>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 68838010>
    <ETag `Caseref'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Caselaw'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `Polyflex (India) Pvt. Ltd. v. CIT [2022] '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `449 ITR 244'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
