    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <Char Tab>
   <String `From 1-6-1992 : Finance Act, 1992 :'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Title'>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 1405489>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String ` The above rule 68B was inserted with effect from June 1, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `1992, to provide a time limit of three years (now extended to four years, see Note below) from the end '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of the financial year in which the order, giving rise to a demand of any tax, interest, fine, penalty or '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `any other sum for the recovery of which the immovable property has been attached, has become con'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `clusive under the provisions of section 245-I or has become final in terms of the provisions of Chap'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ter XX of the Income-tax Act.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 1405495>
  <PgfTag `Para'>
  <ParaLine 
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 1405494>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Char Tab>
   <String `It also provides that the period of three years may be extended by one year in certain cases where '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the sale falls through. Further, it has also been provided to exclude certain period during which the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `order is stayed by any court.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 1405500>
  <PgfTag `Para'>
  <PgfEndCond Yes>
  <PgfCondFullPgf Yes>
  <ParaLine 
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 1405499>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Char Tab>
   <String `Where the sale of the attached immovable property is not effected within the time limit laid down '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `in this rule, the relevant attachment order will be deemed to have been vacated on the expiry of the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `period of limitation.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
   <ElementEnd `Notes'>
