   > # end of Font
   <String `1. Definition'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Emphasis'>
   <String `.—In this Schedule, “transitional previous year” means the period reckoned as the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `previous year for the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 1989, in the manner spec'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ified in sub-section (2) of section 3 and, in a case where the first proviso or the third proviso to that '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `sub-section applies, the longer or, as the case may be, the longest of the periods reckoned in the man'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ner laid down in the said first proviso or, as the case may be, the said third proviso.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
