  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `(1) of the Table below shall be subject to the modification that the reference therein to the amount or '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `amounts specified in the corresponding entry in column (2) of the said Table, shall be construed as a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `reference to the said amount or amounts as increased by multi'>
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `plying each such amount by a fraction '>
  > # end of ParaLine
