   > # end of Font
   <String `7. Power of Board to grant relief in case of hardship.'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Emphasis'>
   <String `—The Board may, if it considers it desirable or '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `expedient so to do for avoiding genuine hardship, by general or special order, grant appropriate '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `relief in any case or class of cases where the transitional previous year is longer than twelve months.'>
