   > # end of Font
   <String ` This clause was inserted by the Finance Act, 2006, with effect from April 1, 2007, i.e., with effect '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `from the assessment year 2007-08. It provides that the fund shall be of an establishment to whom the provisions of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `sub-section (3) or sub-section (4) of section 1 of the Employees’ Provident Funds and Miscellaneous Provisions Act, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `1952, are applicable and such establishment has been exempted under section 17 from the operation of all or any of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the provisions of any scheme referred to in that section.'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FSize  7.5 pt>
    <FLocked No>
    <FSeparation 4>
    <FColor `Blue'>
   > # end of Font
