   <String `From 1-4-2007 : Rationalisation of provisions.'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FPlatformName `W.Arial.R.700'>
    <FWeight `Bold'>
    <FEncoding `FrameRoman'>
    <FSize  7.5 pt>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Title'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FSize  7.5 pt>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 4648271>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` The above proviso was inserted by the Finance Act, 2006, with '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `effect from April 1, 2007, i.e., with effect from the assessment year 2007-08. It provides that in a case where recogni'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tion has been accorded to any provident fund on or before March 31, 2006, and such provident fund does not satisfy '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the conditions set out in rule 4(ea), and any other conditions which the Board may, by rules specify in this behalf, the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `recognition to such fund shall be withdrawn, if such fund does not satisfy such conditions on or before March 31, 2007 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `(extended to March 31, 2008, by the Finance Act, 2007 and now extended to March 31, 2009 by Finance Act, 2008).'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FSize  7.5 pt>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementEnd `Notes'>
