   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 1479805>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String ` Clause (ea) of rule 4, which was inserted by the Finance Act, 2006, was substituted to provide that the fund shall '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `be a fund of an establishment to which the provisions of sub-section (3) of section 1 of the Employees’ Provident Funds '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and Miscellaneous Provisions Act, 1952, apply or of an establishment which has been notified by the Central Provident '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Fund Commissioner under sub-section (4) of section 1 of the said Act, and such establishment shall obtain exemption '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
